name: USNetwork
description:
The USNetwork DAO is a new rideshare and delivery service. 

 Our customers are our focal point we promise to provide you with the best service available. 
 
 Our drivers and shoppers or "Service Members" earn 97% of the funds paid. Based on their "Customer Delivery Rating" or CDR, Service members increase levels based on the total time in the achieved level. 

 The rating system is based on the swipe system. A left swipe < for a horrible experience and right > on an excellent experience.
payDisclosure: Thank you for funding the USNetworkDAO.
